2500|$|Abnaa el-Balad ( [...] , Sons of the Land or Sons and Daughters of the Country or People of the Homeland Movement) is {{a secular}} {{movement}} {{made up of}} Palestinians, {{most of whom are}} Arab citizens of Israel. The stated goals of the movement are: the return of all Palestinian refugees, an end to <b>Israeli's</b> <b>occupation</b> of territories and the establishment of a democratic, secular Palestinian state.|$|R
